                "label": "Quick launch behaviour",
                "description": "What to do when Clawd is launched via Quick Launch. If 'start conversation' is selected, Clawd will start listening immediately. If 'stay open' is chosen, Clawd will quit after a minute of inactivity. If 'open home screen' is chosen, Clawd will behave the same as if launched from the app launcher.",
